{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sauna of the DEAD</strong> is an action RPG where you become a heatwave master in Japanese-style sauna, swinging your towel to blast hot air at zombies and demons in the underworld's saunas to defeat them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The saunas of the underworld are, surprisingly, Japanese-style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780140/extras/sauna_store_atk_low_x2.gif?t=1736665994\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a heatwave master, you were lured by a suspicious man to work in the underworld's saunas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over a 7-day stay in the underworld, defeat many zombies and demons to aim for a showdown with the Demon King Vihta.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780140/extras/sauna_campfire_title_8.jpg?t=1736665994\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Swing your towel to hurl hot air at zombies and demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Use different towel swinging techniques to defeat many zombies and demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Collect Totonoi orbs to power up through Sauna &gt; Cold Bath &gt; Lounging Rest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Receive rewards based on the number of defeats, and power up with sauna goods and drinks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780140/extras/sauna_campfire_title_7.png?t=1736665994\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 to 6 hours </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* You can enjoy the game even more by aiming for the top ranks in Endless Summer leaderboard, which is part of the endgame content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780140/extras/sauna_campfire_title_1.png?t=1736665994\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sauna terminology</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Aufguss involves swinging a towel in the sauna to generate hot air and directing that hot air towards the sauna's patrons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Loyly refers to the act of pouring water on hot stones in the sauna to create steam and increase the sauna's temperature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- In this game, &quot;to be put in order&quot; means to achieve a state of mindfulness and emptiness by repeatedly going through the cycle of Sauna &gt; Cold Bath &gt; Rest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780140/extras/sauna_campfire_title_6.png?t=1736665994\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Streaming is permitted for both individuals and corporations without the need for permission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monetization is only allowed using the functions provided by the video streaming sites.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We appreciate including the game's name in the title of the video or stream and linking to the Steam page in the description.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We take no responsibility for any damages incurred by streaming this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The contents of these guidelines are subject to change without notice.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Heatwave Master Who Ascends Zombie King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2780140/3bb39fd4eea50b22a9905b39a010974d94da5d7f.jpg"},{"name":"Heatwave Master Who Ascends Demon Queen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2780140/71bc8ebf4fbff1c295ff94